 <summary>SmartServoGui helps you scan for servo devices easily view and tweak their settings!</summary>
 <description>
   <p>
   SmartServoGui is a fully featured Qt GUI application that helps you discover
   devices on available serial links, get an overview of all of their registers,
   and easily tweak their settings!
